ActIndian Act
SubjectWasagamack Indian Reserve, Manitoba ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise of the power of Manitoba to take 140.4 hectares (346.92 acres) of lands in WASAGAMACK INDIAN RESERVE; and (2) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of these lands, for the purpose of an all weather public highway in northern Manitoba.
